(387, 1, '2018-11-30 10:19:29', '2018-11-30 10:19:29', 'THE 29 year old Air force of Zimbabwe pilot, Tashinga Musonza who allegedly murdered his 32 year old lawyer girlfriend Lucy Dube on Sunday has been freed.\r\n\r\nLucy Dube was a lawyer working for the Gweru Legal Aid Directorate.<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\nGweru court magistrate ordered his immediate release saying police over detained the accused in violation of his constitutional rights.\r\nThe accused was detained for 53 hours instead of 48 hours as required by the constitution, Court said. It took police 53 hours to take the accused from Gweru Central Police to the Magistrates Court which a just a stones throw away.\r\nMusonza assaulted the late Dube to work after suspecting that she was having a relationship with a soldier also based in Gweru.</span>', 'Gweru pilot who killed \'cheating\' girlfriend freed', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'gweru-pilot-who-killed-cheating-girlfriend-freed', '', '', '2018-11-30 16:44:13', '2018-11-30 16:44:13', '', 0, 'http://www.zimskynews.com/?p=387', 0, 'post', '', 0),
