(565, 4, '2019-02-11 11:17:55', '2019-02-11 11:17:55', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Deputy Minister of information Energy Mutodi has revealed that Vice president Constantino Chiwengas heath scare is nothing but a minor stomach ailment</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This follows after <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://iharare.com/vps-chiwenga-mohadi-flown-out/\" target=\"_blank\">Chiwenga was flown to India</a>for medical attention after another stint in South African, not more than 2 days before.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://iharare.com/pictures-vp-chiwengas-unhealthy-appearance-sets-tongues-wagging/\" target=\"_blank\">VP Chiwenga</a>set tongues wagging after appearing on national  television declaring he was fit, further fanning the flames that his health woes were far from over.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However Mutodi said all is well with the VP.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The Hon. Vice President CDN Chiwenga is recovering well from some minor abdominal ailment in Delhi, India. Meanwhile, His Excellency President ED Mnangagwa has secured lucrative deals that will make a difference to the economy &amp; provide jobs to the youths.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->', 'Mutodi gives update on VP Chiwenga\'s medical trip to India', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'mutodi-gives-update-on-vp-chiwengas-medical-trip-to-india', '', '', '2019-02-11 11:17:55', '2019-02-11 11:17:55', '', 0, 'http://www.zimskynews.com/?p=565', 0, 'post', '', 0),
