(595, 2, '2019-02-12 09:15:13', '2019-02-12 09:15:13', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>FINANCE and Economic Development Minister Professor Mthuli Ncube, has trashed claims by MDC Alliance deputy chairperson and former Finance Minister Tendai Biti that Government will this week introduce a new currency.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Biti yesterday tweeted: The regime will this week introduce a new Zimbabwe currency not backed by any #reserves &amp; without the context of structural reforms which is a prerequisite for currency reform. That move is pure undiluted #insanity. An unbanked currency is just the #bond note by another name.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Addressing the media on the sidelines of a tour of Nestl, Prof Ncube said Biti was entitled to his own opinion, but Government had set procedures and timelines to deal with the currency matter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well, he is not in Government, but it is up to him to say whatever he wants to say, he said. He is free to comment and say anything.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He is a member of the opposition so that is always welcome. It keeps us on our toes, but we have policies, we will do it when we are ready. But we have a game plan, a roadmap and we will do it when the conditions are right.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof Ncube reiterated that Government would be in a position to clearly enunciate the currency reforms in 12 months.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I cannot give a timeline, I have always consistently said in 12 months time we should have done a lot in reforming our currency and monetary system and I still maintain that, he said.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof Ncube was on record saying Government was working on introducing a currency that would be stable and less volatile.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He said dealing with the fiscal side was the first order towards a stable currency.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=Mthuli%20Ncube%20trashes%20Biti%20https%3A%2F%2Fzoomzimbabwe.com%2F2019%2F02%2F12%2Fmthuli-ncube-trashes-biti%2F\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"sms://?&amp;body=Mthuli%20Ncube%20trashes%20Biti https%3A%2F%2Fzoomzimbabwe.com%2F2019%2F02%2F12%2Fmthuli-ncube-trashes-biti%2F\"></a></em><ins> </ins></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mthuli Ncube denies new currency introduction claims', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'mthuli-ncube-denies-new-currency-introduction-claims', '', '', '2019-02-12 09:15:13', '2019-02-12 09:15:13', '', 0, 'http://www.zimskynews.com/?p=595', 0, 'post', '', 0),
